author: imirish2016
title: Classy hotel, great service.
text: We come in every year for St Patrick's day. Lovely hotel located near 5th ave. Cafe Milano, around the corner is great Italian food. An bon pain is a nice coffee shop also around the corner. Minus 5 ice bar is across the street, and MOMA is also across the street.
